Git - Installation on Linux
Command to install
# yum install git
Command to verify the installation
# git  --version
How to check the configuration of git 
# git config --list
How to configure a user name
# git config --global user.name <name>
# git config --global user.email <email_id>
How to create the project or Local Repo in git
# git init <project_name>
How to check your git status
# git status 






